text: Grosvenor Square is a large garden square in the exclusive Mayfair district of London, England. It is the property of the Duke of Westminster. There is a 9/11 memorial and statues of American presidents like Franklin D. Roosevelt and Ronald Reagan. Grosvenor Square is the location of the American embassy in England. == Related pages == * List of botanical gardens Category:Buildings and structures in the City of Westminster
